Welcome to example.com, <%= @user.first_name %>
===============================================

You have successfully signed up to overattired.com,
your username is: <%= @user.email %>.

To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.

    <h1> YOUR MATHCES </h1>

    <% @user.get_initial_matches.each do |category, matches| %>
      <ul>
        <li><%= category.to_s %></li>
          <% matches.each do |match| %>
          <ul>
            <li><%= match.title %></li>
            <li><%= match.subtitle %></li>
            <li>Category: <%= match.category %></li>
            <li><a href="<%= match.url %>">Product Link: <%= match.url %></a></li>
            <img width="50px" height="100px" src="<%= match.image_url %>">
            <li>Price: $<%= match.price %></li>
            <li>Size: <%= match.size %></li>
            <li>Decade: <%= match.when_made %></li>
            <li>Description: <%= match.description %></li>
          </ul>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% end %>

Thanks for joining and have a great day!
